Package: scPloidyR
Title: Single-Cell Copy Number Calling via Hidden Markov Models
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("scPloidyR Authors", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  email = "noreply@example.com")
Description: Implements a Hidden Markov Model (HMM) for detecting copy number
    states from single-cell sequencing data using depth and B-allele frequency
    (BAF) observations. Supports per-chromosome fitting, reference-aware
    parameter learning, and parallel multi-cell processing.
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0)
Imports: parallel, stats, utils
Suggests: testthat (>= 3.0.0)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Config/testthat/edition: 3
